## Demo Data

The system automatically seeds demo data including:
- Demo user (demo@portfolioai.com / demo123)
- Sample brokerage accounts
- Mock holdings (AAPL, GOOGL, TSLA, MSFT, NVDA)
- Sample transactions
- Portfolio snapshots

## Testing

### Run Backend Tests
```bash
cd backend
pytest tests/ -v
```

### Run ML Model Training
```bash
cd ml-models/src
python train_sentiment.py
python train_price_signal.py
python export_coreml.py
```

### Build iOS App
```bash
cd ios-app
xcodebuild -project PortfolioAI.xcodeproj -scheme PortfolioAI -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name=iPhone 15' build
```
